OL,3,C'Depraved' killer jailed for 24 years
OL,5,FA man who murdered, dismembered and
OL,6,Fdumped his friend's body parts in a
OL,7,FTyrone reservoir in 2022 has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to a minimum of 24 years in
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FStephen McCourt (41) of Riverview in
OL,12,FAugher was convicted of murdering
OL,13,FDamien Heagney in what has been
OL,14,Fdescribed as a gruesome and callous
OL,15,Fkilling.
OL,17,FHis family said they had been through
OL,18,Fa torturous ordeal and struggled to
OL,19,Fovercome the gruesome manner in which
OL,20,Ftheir loved one was murdered.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
