OL,5,FThe trial judge described the killing
OL,6,Fas "ferocious".
OL,8,FMr Heagney's arms, head and legs were
OL,9,Frecovered in plastic bags from Cappagh
OL,10,Freservoir by specialist divers in
OL,11,FAugust 2022. His torso was never found.
OL,13,FDuring sentencing the judge told the
OL,14,Fcourt family impact statements
OL,15,Fdescribed the "pain, sorrow and loss"
OL,16,Fthey had suffered.
