OL,5,F"I have watched them sit through the
OL,6,Ftrial with dignity and resilience and
OL,7,Flisten to what was harrowing evidence.
OL,8,FI know your lives will never be the
OL,9,Fsame," he said at Friday's sentencing.
OL,11,FThe 45-year-old Cookstown man
OL,12,Fdisappeared in December 2021.
OL,14,FThe prosecution claimed McCourt was
OL,15,Fthe last person to see Mr Heagney
OL,16,Falive and he stabbed him multiple
OL,17,Ftimes in the head following a quarrel
OL,18,Fbefore placing his body parts in
OL,19,Fplastic bags and throwing them into
OL,20,Fthe water in a bid to cover up his
OL,21,Fcrime.
