OL,5,FA family statement said: "The last few
OL,6,Fyears have been torturous for our
OL,7,Ffamily.
OL,9,F"No one should ever have to deal with
OL,10,Fthe heartache of losing a son and a
OL,11,Fbrother, yet we have to wake up every
OL,12,Fsingle morning knowing that Damien was
OL,13,Fmurdered.
OL,15,F"Damien's life was taken so cruelly,
OL,16,Fand the actions that followed were
OL,17,Fdepraved ` more than we can ever begin
OL,18,Fto express.
