OL,5,FA senior PSNI officer said the murder
OL,6,Fof Damien Heagney was the "most
OL,7,Fsenseless loss of a life."
OL,9,FDetective Superintendent Rachel Wilson
OL,10,Fsaid: "While the exact cause of Mr
OL,11,FHeagney's death has never been
OL,12,Fdetermined due to the decomposition of
OL,13,Fhis remains, the post-mortem did
OL,14,Fidentify possible stab wounds to his
OL,15,Fhead, neck, arms and legs.
OL,17,F"This was the most senseless loss of a
OL,18,Flife.
