OL,5,F"It was a murder made even more
OL,6,Fdisturbing by the way in which Mr
OL,7,FHeagney's body was subsequently
OL,8,Fdismembered, concealed in a number of
OL,9,Fpackages, and ultimately disposed of
OL,10,Fin a reservoir.
OL,12,F"These actions were callous, cruel and
OL,13,Fbrutal beyond comprehension.
OL,15,F"Today, working in partnership with
OL,16,Fthe Public Prosecution Service and
OL,17,Fthanks to the support of NI Water,
OL,18,Finternal police teams and members of
OL,19,Fthe public, Stephen McCourt has
OL,20,Ffinally been held accountable.
